featured_reviews.review_id:
Masjid is a place of prayer for Muslims. Mosques are usually covered buildings, but can be any place where prayers are performed, including outdoor courtyards. This masjid is really very good and peaceful. This is a house of Allah.
May Allah give toufik to perform 5 times daily prayer in the masjid.
